g.title: IProcessor
g.text: It has zero or more input ports
and zero or more output ports

g.title: ISink
g.text: Has single input port and not putput ports
Consumes data that has passed to its input port

g.title: ISource
g.text: Has no input ports and single output put
Generates data itself and pushed it to

g.title: ForkProcessor
g.text: Has one input and many outputs
Pulls data from input nand copies

g.title: ConcatProcessor
g.text: Has many inputs and only one putput
Pulls all data from first input util
then all data from second input etc
and pushed all data to output
